[ laughing ]

27:06.520 --> 27:09.257
I'm having fun, daddy.
I am too, sweetheart.

27:09.323 --> 27:11.692
Are you coming home to stay,
daddy?

27:11.759 --> 27:15.463
Okay, toots, your brother's
asleep. Now it's your turn
for bed, okay?

27:15.529 --> 27:18.532
Do I have to?
Yes, you have to.

27:18.599 --> 27:20.534
Come on.
Daddy!

27:20.601 --> 27:23.104
<i>Just a couple more minutes?
Peter! Listen, honey.</i>

27:23.170 --> 27:25.539
I'll give you a kiss
after your daddy
tucks you in, okay?

27:25.606 --> 27:29.176
Yeah. I'll give you
a piggyback ride.
You ready?

27:29.243 --> 27:32.413
Mount up.
[ indistinct ]

27:32.480 --> 27:36.417
okay, here we go.
[ Mimicking HORSE Galloping ]

27:52.967 --> 27:55.970
god, it's amazing how Megan
and Timothy are growing.

27:56.037 --> 27:58.673
I found the check.
Who's Jill Roberts?

27:58.739 --> 28:01.576
A friend of mine from work.
I didn't tell her
what it was for.

28:01.642 --> 28:03.611
Thank you.

28:05.046 --> 28:07.048
Look, Myra,
I've been thinking.

28:07.114 --> 28:09.116
I know how hard all This
is gonna be on you.

28:09.183 --> 28:12.753
If you want me to,
I'll be there
during the Abortion.

28:12.820 --> 28:14.755
No. I don't think
I want you there.

28:14.822 --> 28:19.093
<i>[ Megan ]
mommy, I'm ready to say my
prayers. Is daddy still here?</i>

28:19.160 --> 28:21.062
No, Honey.
Daddy's just left.

