28:45.786 --> 28:47.788
I don't see anybody from
the department of surgery.

28:47.855 --> 28:50.024
You really expected anyone
with any brains to show up?

28:50.091 --> 28:52.560
<i>[ Laughs ]
Ooh, look here.</i>

28:52.627 --> 28:54.829
Have Another hors D'oeuvre,
Shirley.
No.

28:54.895 --> 28:56.831
Stick something in
your mouth, will you?

28:56.898 --> 28:59.867
Just think, I could be home
scrubbing my kitchen floor.

28:59.934 --> 29:02.470
You'll do anything to get
on your knees, won't you?

29:02.536 --> 29:05.006
Ehrlich, this comes from
the bottom of my heart:

29:05.072 --> 29:08.876
You're a pig.
Let's not get nasty,
Shirley.

29:08.943 --> 29:12.413
I think there's some people
here from the hospital
that you might know.

29:12.480 --> 29:14.448
Good. At last,
a friendly face.

29:14.515 --> 29:16.450
Hi, guys.
Where's Robert?

29:16.517 --> 29:19.153
Are you kidding?
He wouldn't be caught dead
at something like this.

29:19.220 --> 29:21.389
If I'd known you were coming,
I wouldn't have had to
scrape up a date.

29:21.455 --> 29:23.391
Thanks a lot, Diphthong.

29:23.457 --> 29:26.928
Hey, what time we got?
Mmm, a little after 7:00.

29:26.994 --> 29:29.630
I think I feel
a headache coming on.
Okay, okay.

29:29.697 --> 29:32.733
