29:38.105 --> 29:43.110
Uh, may I have everyone's
attention, please?
Thank you.

29:43.177 --> 29:46.981
It's a rare privilege for me...

29:47.048 --> 29:51.352
to be able to open my home
to such a distinguished guest--

29:51.419 --> 29:53.354
Maybe I should say "Brother,"

29:53.421 --> 29:56.791
because in the medical world,
boundaries don't exist.

29:56.857 --> 30:01.529
<i>But then, just let me
say to you, Dr. Sven holstrum,</i>

30:01.596 --> 30:05.333
<i>valkommen, valkommen, valkommen.
[ Chuckles ]</i>

30:05.399 --> 30:08.703
[ speaking swedish ]

30:14.108 --> 30:16.677
- [ swedish ]
- [ repeats in Swedish ]

30:16.744 --> 30:20.414
<i>- [ sven speaking swedish ]
- [ laughing ]</i>

30:20.481 --> 30:23.417
he doesn't speak english?
Caught me by surprise too.

30:23.484 --> 30:26.887
Much traffic?
Don't start with me. Ah.

30:29.523 --> 30:32.260
[ groans ]
I hate this.
I don't want another Drink.

30:32.326 --> 30:34.762
Hey, these two are mine.

30:43.671 --> 30:46.073
I don't know, Luther.
Hey, it's my birthday.

30:46.140 --> 30:48.075
I still don't think
it's a good idea.

30:48.142 --> 30:50.344
Opportunity only knocks
a few times.

30:50.411 --> 30:52.980
And you gotta take advantage
while the Fire's hot.

30:53.047 --> 30:55.049
